The reason for the St. Petersburg delay is connected, among other things, with the constant reshuffle in the tourist block of the government, which does not contribute to coordinated work.
According to experts, if st. Petersburg hotels are not enough for everyone, that most likely you will have to pay attention to regional hotels and rest homes.
Following the example of the celebration of the 300th anniversary of St. Petersburg, the river fleet can be mobilized to the city, that is, the guests of the tournament will be able to live in cabins.
In addition, many fans will arrive in vans in which it will be possible to spend the night.
"The main thing is not to set up so many hotels so that later they are empty," Gennady Lamshin is sure.
Also, rented housing will be very popular during the football championship.
Most likely, the city will create a reserve of rented apartments.
