It was possible to find the man after a helicopter joined the search operations.
On that day, vitaly Alexandrovich, as usual, went to the forest for oats and birch trees, but did not return by the evening.
Relatives immediately asked for help, and the very next day rescuers and caring residents from a neighboring village - about 30 people in total - were raised to search for the mushroom picker.
On the fifth day, they were joined by a helicopter of the fire and rescue center.
