The Volgograd Governor and the Akim of the West Kazakhstan region signed a cooperation agreement.
On September 16, the XII Forum of Interregional Cooperation between Russia and Kazakhstan opened in Sochi.
The key topic is cooperation in the field of agro-industrial complex and ensuring food security.
The Governor of the Volgograd Region Andrey Bocharov is also taking part in the international forum.
